---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Biohacking Tools: Exopod & Wolfpack Hiking — EmpowerX3"
  description="Explore the Exopod recovery chamber and the Wolfpack Hiking Group — the off-road upgrades and convoy that make the journey better."
>

  <!-- ─── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-gray-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-gray-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Ancillary Tools</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 max-w-3xl leading-tight">
        Off-Road Upgrades & the Convoy You Travel With
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Every serious road trip needs the right add-ons — a lift kit, skid plates, a winch — and
        a convoy of people who have your back when the terrain gets rough. EmpowerX3's ancillary
        tools deliver both.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Exopod ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            Recovery Technology
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-6">
            The Exopod: Your On-Board Recovery System
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Think of the Exopod as the off-road suspension upgrade for your recovery. When you push
            the body hard — intense training, high stress, illness — you need a system that absorbs
            the shock and gets you back on the road fast.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The Exopod combines advanced recovery modalities in a single, accessible session:
            photobiomodulation, targeted heat/cold cycling, and atmospheric optimization. The result
            is faster cellular repair, reduced systemic inflammation, and measurably better HRV
            within 72 hours.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            It's not a luxury — it's a force multiplier. The right suspension means you can take on
            rougher terrain without destroying the chassis.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            {[
              'Accelerated muscle and tissue recovery',
              'Mitochondrial photobiomodulation',
              'Inflammation reduction — measurable via biomarkers',
              'Improved sleep architecture post-session',
              'Available to EmpowerX3 clients through partner facilities',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
                <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-brand-700 transition-colors">
            Ask About Exopod Access
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-10 border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <span class="text-8xl block mb-6" aria-hidden="true">🛸</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Exopod Sessions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Available at partner facilities — ask Gary about scheduling during your onboarding call.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── Wolfpack ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 bg-white rounded-2xl p-10 border border-brand-100 text-center">
          <span class="text-8xl block mb-6" aria-hidden="true">🐺</span>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">The Wolfpack</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Monthly hikes. Real terrain. Real accountability. Real community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            Community
          </span>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Wolfpack Hiking Group: The Convoy That Has Your Back
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            No cross-country road trip is better alone. The best ones have a convoy — other drivers
            who know the route, share the load, and pull you out when you're stuck in the mud.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The Wolfpack Hiking Group is EmpowerX3's community component. Monthly group hikes —
            real terrain, real exertion, real conversation. It's where clients test their rebuilt
            engines against actual mountains and discover that the protocols work.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            There's something that happens when you summit a trail you couldn't have walked
            six months ago. Lab numbers become lived experience. The Wolfpack is where
            the theory meets the trail.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-8">
            {[
              'Monthly guided hikes — beginner to advanced terrain',
              'Group accountability and peer coaching',
              'Post-hike recovery review and biometric check-in',
              'Private community channel for daily support',
              'Exclusive to active EmpowerX3 clients',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm">
                <span class="text-brand-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-brand-600 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-brand-700 transition-colors">
            Join the Wolfpack
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
